name: Ekal Nari Shakti Sansthan
briefDescription: Ekal Nari Shakti Sansthan is Located in UDAIPUR AND Kota, Rajasthan.The Association of Strong Women Alone (ASWA)  is a registered Society, formed and led by low-income Single Women.  It implements its mission and objectives through a Mass Membership Based Group of Single Women, with an organizational structure from the Village / Gram Panchayat Level to the State Level.  The Structure is strong, and the objectives of the organization are effectively implemented.
